title: In The Blink Of An Eye (A Complete Dark & Synthwave BGM Pack)
description: The 13-track electronic album In The Blink Of An Eye combines synthwave, dark ambient, industrial, and noise music and blend them all together.
longDescription:
The 13-track electronic album In The Blink Of An Eye combines synthwave, dark ambient, industrial, and noise music and blend them all together. The album trailer can be watched here.


This album is packed with action themes, general background tracks, chase themes and a main menu theme. 7 out of 13 songs in the album can be looped, and the tracks that can be looped are named as:


- I Hear Their Footsteps (Action 01)

- Time Is A Multiplier (Action 03)

- In The Blink Of An Eye (Action 04)

- One Step Further (General Ambiance 02)

- Somethings You Can't Walk Away From (Chase Theme 01)

- Not A Job For -Piece Of Cakers- (Chase Theme 04)

- Encrypted (Main Menu Theme)


Total album duration: 42 Minutes

Does album loop?: Majority of the album

Is attribution necessary?: No
technicalDetails:
